---
const hotels = [
  {
    name: 'Hotel Nombre 1',
    stars: '★★★★',
    address: 'Calle Ejemplo, 10 · Ceuta',
    phone: '+34 956 000 000',
    web: '#',
  },
  {
    name: 'Hotel Nombre 2',
    stars: '★★★★',
    address: 'Calle Ejemplo, 24 · Ceuta',
    phone: '+34 956 000 001',
    web: '#',
  },
  {
    name: 'Hotel Nombre 3',
    stars: '★★★',
    address: 'Calle Ejemplo, 5 · Ceuta',
    phone: '+34 956 000 002',
    web: '#',
  },
];
---
<section id="alojamiento" class="accommodation-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">Alojamiento</h2>
    <div class="section-divider reveal"><span>✦</span></div>

    <p class="accommodation-intro reveal">
      Para facilitar vuestra estancia, os proponemos algunos hoteles cercanos a la finca.
      La disponibilidad en la zona es limitada, así que os animamos a reservar con antelación.
    </p>

    <div class="hotel-grid">
      {hotels.map(h => (
        <div class="hotel-card reveal">
          <p class="hotel-stars">{h.stars}</p>
          <h3 class="hotel-name">{h.name}</h3>
          <p class="hotel-address">{h.address}</p>
          <a href={`tel:${h.phone.replace(/\s/g, '')}`} class="hotel-phone">{h.phone}</a>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .accommodation-section {
    padding: var(--section-padding);
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .accommodation-intro {
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .hotel-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.2rem;
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .hotel-card {
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    text-align: center;
    transition: border-color 0.25s, box-shadow 0.25s;
  }

  .hotel-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(184,147,106,0.1);
  }

  .hotel-stars {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .hotel-name {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .hotel-address {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .hotel-phone {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .hotel-phone:hover { color: var(--color-accent-dark); }

  @media (max-width: 680px) {
    .hotel-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; max-width: 400px; margin-inline: auto; }
  }
</style>
